OL,3,CMan arrested after reports of fight
OL,4,C'involving gun' in city centre
OL,6,FA man has been arrested and city
OL,7,Fstreets cordoned off after police were
OL,8,Fcalled to reports of a man with a gun.
OL,10,FPolice were called after reports a man
OL,11,Fwas threatening another with a firearm
OL,12,Fduring a fight in Clayton Square, in
OL,13,FLiverpool city centre, at around
OL,14,F4.45am on 6 April.
OL,16,FThere is "no suggestion" that a
OL,17,Ffirearm was used and no reports of any
OL,18,Finjuries, Merseyside Police added.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
