OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775499063
OL,3,CMan arrested after reports of fight
OL,4,C'involving gun' in city centre
OL,6,FA man, 37, was arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof possession of a firearm without a
OL,8,Fcertificate, and remains in custody.
OL,10,FA BB gun was later recovered and
OL,11,Fseized by officers.
OL,13,FCordons were in place on Ranelagh
OL,14,FStreet, Button Street, Mathew Street,
OL,15,FVictoria Street and part of
OL,16,FWhitechapel, but are now being lifted.
OL,18,FMerseyside Police said enquiries are
OL,19,Fongoing and are appealing for anyone
OL,20,Fwith information to contact them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/2
